<div id="post-1741598" class="blog-post position-4 even-post"><div class="even-post-inner blog-post-inner"><h1 class="title"><a href="http://softwarelivre.org/helioloureiro/blog/feliz-aniversario-debian-25-anos">Feliz aniversário Debian! 25 anos!</a></h1><span class="publishing-info"><span class="date">16 de Agosto de 2018, 9:35</span><span class="author">, por Home</span><span class="comments"> - <a href="/helioloureiro/blog/feliz-aniversario-debian-25-anos#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>sem comentários ainda</span></a></span></span><div>
